T1  - The commodity pattern of trade and the Heckscher-Ohlin theorem in the presence of aggregate and commodity-specific factor-intensity reversals
AU  - Fisher, Franklin M.
AU  - Hillman, Arye L.
JO  - Journal of International Economics
VL  - 17
IS  - 1
SP  - 159
EP  - 172
PY  - 1984
DA  - 1984/08/01/
